    • Constructor Detail

      • TileInfo

        public TileInfo​(int[] deltas,
                double[] times)
        Initialize this new tileInfo with a list for HP deltas for given tiles and associated periods.
        Parameters:
        deltas - An integer list (currently of lenght 4) containing heal/damage done by a certain tile (gas, water, lava and nonwater).
        times - A double list (currently of lenght 4) containing the time periods for the damage done by a certain tile (gas, water, lava and nonwater).
